longBusinessSummary: Fastbase, Inc. operates as a data and web analytics SaaS company worldwide. Its SaaS solution generates leads reports containing company profiles, visitor interactions, key employee contact data, LinkedIn profile information, and email addresses. Its products include WebLeads tool is a Google Analytics add-on that provides information on web traffic, including web visitor tracking, qualified leads, google analytics, leads in real-time, and verified business contacts; Google Ads Click Identifier that discover who clicks on ads, as well as start google ads campaign and get leads sent directly to inbox daily; Google Business Ads that  generate leads from Google Analytics; and MailAds that put ads in front of potential customer, track and identify ad visitors, and get lists of qualified leads. The company was founded in 2014 and is based in New York, New York.
longName: Universal New Energy Holding Group, Inc.
